Package: ecocrop
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of the EcoCrop model for estimating adaptation of plants to environments
Description: The EcoCrop model estimates environmental suitability for plants using a limiting factor approach for plant growth developed by Hackett (1991) <doi:10.1007/BF00045728>. The implementation in this package is fast and flexible: it allows for the use of any (environmental) predictor variable, both static (e.g. soil pH) and dynamic (monthly climate data).
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2020-04-15
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++11
Imports: meteor, terra (>= 0.5-8), methods (>= 0.2-2), Rcpp (>= 0.12.4)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Authors@R: c(person("Robert J.", "Hijmans", role = c("cre", "aut"), email = "r.hijmans@gmail.com"), person("Rhys", "Manners", role = "ctb"))
